data.meta_description: 19K likes, 0 comments - danielneiditch on June 4, 2023: "Was a special day being an honored guest at the 2023 Israel Day Parade on Fifth Ave in NYC. Today we celebrated against hate and antisemitism. There is no place in this world for hate of any kind. We all must stand together as one no matter what race or religion we are. Everyone must do their part to make the world a better place and respect one another. #israel #israeldayparade #lamborghini #stophate #maketheworldabetterplace".
